  <brief_title>Posthemorrhoidectomy Pain Management With Electronic Bidet or Sitz Bath</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Blind, Randomized Controlled, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Convenience of Electronic Bidet With Very Low Force Flow Fountain System for Pain Control and Wound Healing After Operation for Anal Disease, Compared to Conventional Sitz Bath</official_title>
